Meet Nas, a cornerstone of the Luxe Concept Salon team with over a decade of dedicated service. As one of our most seasoned stylists, Nas brings a wealth of expertise to every client interaction. Specializing in classic cutting and coloring techniques, she effortlessly translates her passion for precision into stunning, personalized hair transformations. Nas’s discerning eye for detail and commitment to excellence have earned her a loyal clientele who trust her to deliver impeccable results every time. Whether crafting a timeless cut, mastering intricate color blends, or creating flawless styles, Nas’s artistry shines through, making her an invaluable asset to our salon.

Availability: Wednesday, Thursday, Friday & Saturday.

excerpt.rendered: With her creative styling skills, precision cutting expertise and keen eye for colour, she offers a high-end, attentive experience.
